<p>Case studies serve double duty. They build trust with prospects and rank for long-tail keywords.</p>
<p>Structure each case study around a searchable problem:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Title:</strong> "How [Industry] Company Reduced IT Costs 40% with Managed Services"</li>
